Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在无须一切顾虑留情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用神器「佩露索娜」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,允许
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全装备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彻底解决
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样…就已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的我和亚拉斯托尔会解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮他找到完美无缺的火雾战士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是留下男人而死去的女人最后的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  威尔艾米娜  提亚玛特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿你们拥有天下无敌的好运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「千征令」奥尔贡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经让炎发灼眼的讨伐者订下契约了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎发灼眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  在她习惯这个世界的这期间里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不隐藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不可以让你逃走是也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说逃走？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既非炎发灼眼的讨伐者也非我是也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彩…彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「彩虹之翼」梅利希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的誓言  重要的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果手下留情的话可伤脑筋了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我先练练手…的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了呢  千征令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙你关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要测试我「虹天剑」的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比你更适合的人选了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  马上结束它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,订下契约时的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这契约并不是什么命运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我选择的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样我还是要自己选择
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条道路…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要想办法从这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要与强者交手…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量正涌出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…这就是火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是赌上生死的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.69,0:07:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是传说中的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该也有什么弱点的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点就能破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:07:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:07:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是「夜笠」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎发灼眼的讨伐者所穿着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我翅膀的一部分化成的黑衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…以赐予强者武具为使命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我自愿成为密斯提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说人类自己成为密斯提斯的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强者…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…寻求与其相称之强者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…自愿成为密斯提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…是指那把大太刀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…铠甲武士「天目一个」和大太刀「贽殿遮那」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有制作这些的刀匠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎这三个人格混杂在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:09:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赐予超越人类的强者注入我生命精华的武具——贽殿遮那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为寻求与之相称的强者  自愿成为密斯提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了寻找那个强者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心甘情愿舍弃作为人的一切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也和我一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以自己的意志  来寻找自己的归属
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一心一意的前进着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将成为你主人的强者…就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都到了这会儿  就不必说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔艾米娜·卡梅尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我只是为了完成与她的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而苟活到现在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么乱来的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真担心刚刚得到的火雾战士就这么失去了也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常清楚只是偶然成功的罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比锻炼还艰苦一百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比红世之徒还可怕…一千倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然说了  就要负起责任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀…看来好像某个家伙被干掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了大规模的崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这感觉是…红世的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小白…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  亚拉斯托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我赢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢的人可以随意处置对方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不像是对所迷上的女人提出的条件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有三条约定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准再吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在扰乱世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽可能的锻炼在我之后出现的炎发灼眼的讨伐者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的决战  虽然很艰苦但尽兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  不等你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「彩虹之翼」梅利希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想见你啊…炎发灼眼的讨伐者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔艾米娜·卡梅尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想一下我们现在身处此地的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来实现她的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…大概只是为了这个…而在一起的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个彻彻底底…令人讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正见证着新时代的来临是也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…新的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天目一个的力量就只有大太刀而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个不应使用自在法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而以格斗去迎战的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与我们红世之徒对战时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光从表面的攻击来判断战斗方式是不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在外表运动的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要感觉内部存在之力的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是察觉自在法的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对外观的警戒也不能放松
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  必须记住的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们红世之徒所操纵的自在法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是会引起任何不可能发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊慌没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意现实存在的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为我们的绝招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和红世有关的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该闭嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔艾米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了新时代的来临是也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我们也该告别了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长久以来承蒙照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:21:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话至今为止的努力便没有意义了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今往后任何事都必须一个人去做了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「没问题」这句话就是这意思是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望务必能够谅解是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要照我们所教的去做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便没有问题是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又和天壤劫火在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无须担心了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔艾米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没我看着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜食也不可以吃得太多…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望紧紧拥抱你是也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那么喜欢吃蜜瓜包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.56,0:22:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.27,0:22:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.29,0:22:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.63,0:22:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不等你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算啥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.95,0:24:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在御崎市出现的调律师卡姆辛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.65,0:24:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于开始行动的「化装舞会」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.54,0:24:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后思念着悠二的一位少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.66,0:24:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了真正的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.95,0:24:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  新的序章
